NETGATE Data Backup v3.0.605 Multilingual Incl Keymaker-CORE

NETGATE Data Backup is an effective tool to backup your files, photos, music and any important data on your PC. With NETGATE Data Backup you can even backup your MySQL/PHP databases from your webpage or your blog. Defragment and backup your registry with one simple click. NETGATE Data Backup supports scheduling of automatic backups at specified time. For extended security user has the option to encrypt or compress backuped files.

INSTALL NOTES:

Use the keymaker to register the application.
